title: Bug 26863[Dialogs] ResourceListSelectionDialog should not do prefix matching when '' specified
description: Bug 26863[Dialogs] ResourceListSelectionDialog should not do prefix matching when '' specified is present.
EB: build I20021121JDT has changed Open Type so that "x" matches all types ending in 'x' (caseinsensitive), rather than all types containing an 'x'.We should change ResourceListSelectionDialog to be consistent.When a '' wildcard is present, avoid adding a free '' at the end.No change if '?'
